dct_title_s: Off Street Bike Facilities Milwaukee County, Wisconsin 2004
dct_description_sm: This line data layer represents off street bike facilities for Milwaukee County, Wisconsin in 2004. The dataset was originally published by the Wisconsin Bicycle Federation on August 10, 2004.[This feature dataset encompassses all data pertaining to off-street bike facilities in Milwaukee County, Wisconsin.]
